'''Ajjed''' neɣ '''asɣan''' d tagrawt n [[tikti|tektiwin]] d tifelsin id yesskanayen iswi n [[tudert]] d [[tallunt]] ɣer wid yettamnen yis, Akken yettwasen tikwal d Taflest yettwaqqnen ar [[tadfersengamt|tedfersengamt]] d [[tisunayin]], Akken yeqqen daɣen d [[tafada|tɣara]]

== [[Tudayt]] ==
[[Tudayt]] d asɣan amezwaru ideg ttamnen medden d akken yella yiwen n [[yillu|yellu]] kan. Isem-is s [[tɛebrit|Thibrut]] ''Yehweh'', [[Udayen]] ur zmiren ara ad bedren isem agi acku ɣur-sen d amuggi (leḥram). Yellu g tudayt ila (yesɛa) iylan i t-yettallen, yuzen [[amazun]] ɣur [[afgan|ifganen]] i wakken ad ttamnen yyis

== [[Tamasiḥit]] ==
G Tamasiḥit, Yakuc d yiwen, iṣubb ɣer medden s wedmaw n bnadem : [[Ɛisa]].

== [[Islam|Lislam]] ==
G lislam, Yakuc d yiwen meɛna ur iṣubb ara, Ɛisa ɣur inselmen d nnbi kan.


